effect_entries.effect: Inflicts regular damage.  Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Attack by one stage.
effect_entries.short_effect: Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Attack by one stage.

あいてに　じゃれついて
こうげきする。　あいての
こうげきを　さげる　ことがある。

상대에게 치근거리며
공격한다. 상대의
공격을 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

Attaque l’ennemi avec un câlin.
Peut diminuer son Attaque.

Der Anwender knuddelt das Ziel und greift es an.
Gelegentlich sinkt dabei auch dessen
Angriffs-Wert.

El Pokémon que lo usa le hace cucamonas al
objetivo y lo ataca. Puede disminuir el Ataque
del objetivo.

Chi la usa attacca il bersaglio con delle carinerie.
Può anche ridurne l’Attacco.

The user plays rough with the target
and attacks it. This may also lower
the target’s Attack stat.
